SYNOPSIS
        string english_list_or(string *asList)

DESCRIPTION
        english_list_or will return a string with comma separated
        list from asList, ending with 'asList[end-1] or asList[end]'

EXAMPLE
        english_list_or(({ "one", "two", "three", "four" })) returns
        "one, two, three or four"

SEE ALSO
        english_list(E)
